column1661: description:["I'm an HR consultant and career coach obsessed with helping people find joy in their work. A bit Pollyanna-ish? Maybe. But we spend far too much time at work to settle. And the world could use a little bit more joy.\r\n\r\nAs a progressive human resources professional
column1662: I believe that HR has an ethical responsibility to ensure employees are treated well and supported. I'm passionate about nurturing strong organizational cultures
